dialogue_name = &"advice"
text = "Sure! To start, you can try equipping your blade and cutting some of those yellow flowers. Then you could sell a couple of the stems to me with some berries and I can perform the saturation if you don't want to attempt it yourself. The book I am selling should have the recipe for it in there, as well as how to make a strength potion."
